---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Onboarding — 7 nap és élesben vagy | BoxBook"
  description="Mi futtatjuk le veled az első hetet — adat-import, beállítás, próbafoglalás, vendég-tájékoztatás. Ingyenes minden csomagban. Te választod a hetet, a 7. napon élesben vagy."
  canonical="/onboarding"
>
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- HERO — közvetlen, sürgető -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink-50 border-b border-ink-200">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 mesh pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.45)]">
          <i data-lucide="calendar-check" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
          Onboarding · ingyenes
        </span>

        <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[1.02]">
          7 nap és <span class="grad-text-strong">élesben vagy.</span><br/>
          Te választod a hetet.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg lg:text-xl text-ink-600 text-pretty leading-relaxed">
          Nem dobunk be a mélyvízbe, nem küldünk linkeket „olvasd el a doksit"-tal. <b class="text-ink-900">Mi futtatjuk le veled</b> az első hetet — adat-import, ár-mátrix, mosóállás-konfig, kollégák, vendég-tájékoztatás. Te csak annyit teszel, hogy igent mondasz.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <a href="#" data-contact-source="DEMO_TRIAL" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink-900 text-white px-7 py-4 text-sm font-extrabold hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(9,9,11,0.45)]">
            <i data-lucide="play" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            Induljon az onboarding-om
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" data-contact-source="CALL_REQUEST" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white text-ink-900 px-7 py-4 text-sm font-bold ring-1 ring-ink-200 hover:bg-ink-50 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            Inkább hívjatok fel
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-[12px] text-ink-500 font-medium">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <i data-lucide="check" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-leaf-600"></i>
            14 napos próba, kártyaadat nélkül
          </span>
          <span class="text-ink-300">·</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <i data-lucide="check" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-leaf-600"></i>
            Felmondás bármikor, kötbér nélkül
          </span>
          <span class="text-ink-300">·</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <i data-lucide="check" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-leaf-600"></i>
            Magyar email + telefon support
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- 7 NAPOS TIMELINE -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="onboarding" class="relative">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-12 fade-up">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink-900 text-white px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">
          Hogyan zajlik
        </span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[1.05]">
          A 7. nap végén már <span class="grad-text-strong">valós online foglalás</span> érkezik.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-0 right-0 top-[78px] h-0.5 grad-bg opacity-30"></div>

        <ol class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-4 lg:gap-3 relative">
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">1</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-700 font-bold">Nap 1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Próbafiók</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Bejelentkezel, megnyitod a saját demo szalonod. 5 perc.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative" style="transition-delay: 40ms">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg">2</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Nap 2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Adat-import</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">CSV / Excel vagy kontakt-export — vendégek, járművek bemennek.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg">3</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Nap 3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Csapat-meghívás</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Munkatársak email-cím alapján, jogosultság-szintekkel.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative" style="transition-delay: 120ms">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">4</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-700 font-bold">Nap 4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Konfigurálás</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Szolgáltatások, ár-mátrix, mosóállás, nyitvatartás. Mi csináljuk.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative" style="transition-delay: 160ms">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg">5</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Nap 5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Próba-foglalás</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Végigjátsszuk a vendég-flow-t. Ha valami nem fittes, finomítjuk.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-5 relative" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg">6</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Nap 6</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Ügyfél-tájékoztatás</h3>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Email kampány a meglévőknek — „mostantól itt foglalsz”. Mi gyártjuk.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-5 relative overflow-hidden" style="transition-delay: 240ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-lg shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">7</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-400 font-bold">Nap 7 · ÉLES</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="relative font-bold tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Élesben</h3>
            <p class="relative mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-white/75 leading-relaxed">Első valós online foglalás. Mi figyeljük, hogy minden simán menjen.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- INLINE CTA-1 a timeline alatt -->
      <div class="mt-12 fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-6 lg:p-7 flex items-start gap-5 flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap">
        <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 shrink-0">
          <i data-lucide="calendar-plus" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
        </span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-lg">Tegyél egy próbát.</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">14 napos teljes próbafiók — pont olyan, mint az éles, csak demo-adatokkal. Ha a 7. nap végére nem érzed, hogy te is élesben menne, kötelezettség nélkül leállsz.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" data-contact-source="DEMO_TRIAL" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink-900 text-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold hover:bg-ink-800 transition-colors shrink-0">
          14 nap ingyen kipróbálom
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- ONBOARDING TARTALOM + INGYENES HÍVÁS -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative bg-ink-50 border-y border-ink-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-stretch">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-7 lg:p-9">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 shrink-0"><i data-lucide="handshake" class="w-6 h-6"></i></span>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-2xl">Minden, ami a 7 napban benne van — ingyen.</h2>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">
                Az onboarding nem egy „itt a videótár, sok sikert" típusú dolog. Konkrét emberekkel, konkrét időpontokkal, a te konkrét vendég-listáddal.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-5 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Vendég + jármű CSV-import (akár 5 000-ig)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Szolgáltatás + ár-mátrix beállítás</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Mosóállás-konfig + nyitvatartás</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Csapat-meghívás + jogosultságok</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Email + SMS sablonok testreszabása</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Első kampány-email a meglévőknek</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Google Naptár szinkron kollégáknak</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600 shrink-0"></i>Számlázz.hu / Billingo bekötés</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-5 text-[12px] text-ink-500">A Pro és Hálózat csomagok mellé <b class="text-ink-900">dedikált onboarding manager</b> jár, aki Slack / WhatsApp-on elérhető a 14 nap alatt.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 fade-up rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-7 lg:p-9 relative overflow-hidden" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
          <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 w-48 h-48 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase ring-1 ring-white/15">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-leaf-400 pulse-dot"></span>
              Még gondolkodsz?
            </span>
            <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter2 leading-tight">30 perces felmérő hívás — ingyen, kötelezettség nélkül.</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
              Nézzünk meg együtt mit kell a szalonodnak. Ha azt látjuk, hogy a BoxBook nem neked való, azt is őszintén megmondjuk. Nem érdek, nem nyomás.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-400"></i>Mi az igazi szűk keresztmetszeted</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-400"></i>Milyen integrációk hiányoznak most</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-400"></i>Hogyan tűzhetünk fel +18% bevételt</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-400"></i>Mire ne költs (igen, ilyen is van)</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" data-contact-source="CALL_REQUEST" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold w-full justify-center hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">
              <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
              Hívás kérése — visszahívunk
              <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            </a>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[11px] text-center text-white/55">Munkaidőben átlag <b class="text-white">~15 perc</b> múlva csengünk.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- ZÁRÓ CTA — direct kérés -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink-900 text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-50 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(at 20% 30%, rgba(132,204,22,0.30), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 70%, rgba(6,182,212,0.25), transparent 50%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.06]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 56px 56px;"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28 text-center">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase">
          <i data-lucide="rocket" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
          Most kezdünk?
        </span>
        <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[0.98]">
          Mi lenne, ha jövő héten már <span class="grad-text">nem te telefonálnál</span>?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-white/75 text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto text-pretty leading-relaxed">
          Minden héten, amit a régi módszerrel csinálsz, 10+ órát hagysz a telefonon. Hét nap múlva már nem.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="#" data-contact-source="DEMO_TRIAL" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-7 py-4 text-sm font-extrabold hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(132,204,22,0.55)]">
            <i data-lucide="play" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            Induljon a 7 napos onboarding
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" data-contact-source="CALL_REQUEST" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white px-7 py-4 text-sm font-bold ring-1 ring-white/15 hover:bg-white/15 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            Inkább beszéljünk először
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-[12px] text-white/55">14 napos próba · kártyaadat nélkül · felmondás 1 kattintással</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
